snippet.textDisplay:
Was going nice and steady till they ruined it with the guitars and drums. So far this season is not blending the music with the mood. Even the singing styles of singers is not fusing properly. So, for example, at one time the mood is slow, then suddenly its WHAM BAM everyone screaming.WTF?. Why not Abida+RFAK, Ali Azmat+Umair Jaswal etc? The previous coke studios separated the sufis, the rockstars, the popstars and whatnot and gave them a proper platform. 

Now don't lecture me like 'why don't you direct your own music?' I am simply voicing my opinion as a general consumer of music and tbh this downfall of coke studio is worrying me.
